<h2>Town Editor</h2>
<p>Use this page to add/delete/edit towns shown on the maps.
Changed values are highlighted in grey. Use R button to reset value.
{if $dbarr}
Use the G(et) and P(ut) buttons for data transfer from/to the edit line.
{/if}
